title: Nicky Jam Interview and more
itunes:title: Nicky Jam Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had producer Nicky Jam call up where he spoke about the trials and tribulations he experienced while coming up in the music industry and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Lousianna officers who did warrant search at the wrong house and shot and killed a young woman and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
